test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (4 == 3)
 +  where 4 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x7771cd497600>([-3])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7771cd497600> = [[1, -3], [1, -3, 1], [-3], [-3, 1], [1, -3], [1, -3, 1], ...].count
test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert 3 == -3
 +  where 3 = <built-in function prod>([-1, -3])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
